welcome_message_body: "Welcome to White Marsh, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and rich history. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that this wonderful city has to offer during your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to private and chartered flights, offering a more personalized and exclusive experience.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Baltimore/Washington International Thurgood Marshall Airport houses the majority of the airport's facilities, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and various shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is a satellite terminal at BWI Airport that primarily serves Southwest Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is a satellite terminal at BWI Airport that primarily serves American Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is a satellite terminal at BWI Airport that primarily serves Delta Air Lines and its partners.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal at Lee Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to handling cargo flights at Lee Airport.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminals.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Tipton AAF Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.
